      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Evaluation\n\nMAE (Mean Absolute Error): ~1.15\nInterpretation: On average, our forecast is off by\nonly 1.15 taxi rides per zone per 15 minutes.\nRMSE (Root Mean Squared Error): ~4.03\nInterpretation: Low RMSE indicates we aren't\nmaking massive outliers errors.",
